d with external price feeds. The hybrid model balances order book depth with AMM liquidity, creating funding rates that reflect both trader positioning and market-wide LINK sentiment. JIT liquidity auctions can temporarily spike funding costs during volatile periods when additional liquidity enters the system."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
